      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY PADDY BOY (6) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (22.82) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has first look at box 6 this time. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won four of seven tries. Overdue and expected to feature again. SUNSET ESTRELLA (5) flew the lids with a fast early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (22.75) over 400m at this track. Has ability and is one of the better chances. ELITE CRACKER (8) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 3rd over 400m at this track beaten 7 lengths (22.86) behind Another Jimmy in a Grade 4/5 on May 29. Bold showing expected. LITTLE DITZY (1) was in the money last time at this track (22.66) in a Grade 5, finishing a 1.3 lengths third. Has an unbeaten record from this draw, scoring two times.",
